when the money is on the line.

00:50:23.280 --> 00:50:27.790
How does your approach differ
when the money is on the line?

00:50:27.790 --> 00:50:29.900
KENNY WERNER: OK,
well, first of all, we

00:50:29.900 --> 00:50:31.710
were talking about
practicing something.

00:50:31.710 --> 00:50:33.840
Like meditation, you
don't practice it

00:50:33.840 --> 00:50:36.090
